  "subject": "Improved error handling for remote ansible executor.   - Aligned error status with AWX job details status; i.e. lowercase   - Fixed error message in Validation module; encountered during debug.   - Added better handling of inventory name resolution failure.   - Now supports json endpoint selector values, via DSL.",
